{"TopicId":214165,"ForumId":136,"TopicTitle":"Font Sizes","CreatedByName":"pmoffitt","CreatedById":202730,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T05:25:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"pmoffitt","CreatedById":202730,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T05:25:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, I am old, my eye sight sucks and probably need new glasses....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way to change the size of the font in the HUD so I can actually read it?\u00A0 Or add an option to do so.\u00A0 Maybe even some contrast settings for the text.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t get me wrong, I hate to make some of that bigger as realestate is important.\u00A0 But, I really would like to be able to read things at times without giving myself a headach from straining so hard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sitting Duck","CreatedById":200432,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T14:58:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re definitely not the only one. I\u0027d love the option to increase the text size. I\u0027m playing at 1440p on a 32\u0022 monitor, using reading glasses, and it\u0027s still not enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSide bonus: Even better if we could ditch the ugly pixelated look of the interface.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T20:41:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224249860\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022214165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677769100\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200432\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sitting Duck\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Sitting Duck said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSide bonus: Even better if we could ditch the ugly pixelated look of the interface.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about those of us that like it? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vorg","CreatedById":74652,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T20:42:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot so much the size as the style. Makes it harder to read.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224250235\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022214165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677789669\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about those of us that like it? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s 2023, Time to dump EGA graphics\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T20:47:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224250236\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022214165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677789746\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274652\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vorg\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Vorg said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s 2023, Time to dump EGA graphics\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the retro look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sitting Duck","CreatedById":200432,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T22:19:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224250239\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022214165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677790068\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the retro look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo me, it doesn\u0027t look \u0022retro\u0022 - it just looks broken. But definitely to each their own.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njlipinski1","CreatedById":227243,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-03T20:37:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe shader and pixelization on the navball makes the heading numbers really hard to read too, so it\u0027s hard to know which direction to turn using just instruments. I\u0027d also appreciate larger numbers on that \u0026amp; maybe have a toggle to remove the shading. The navball in ksp 1 was much easier to read.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The1Paxman","CreatedById":221380,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-28T17:41:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022To each his own\u0022 is great, so they need to make these things a switchable option.\u003Cbr\u003E\nSome of the lettering is way too small and some of the lettering is way to big.\u00A0 Kerning is off in some places, spacing is way too much in other places.\u00A0 All of the text needs a visual overall, but perhaps the programming is the hard part.\u00A0 On my 1920x1080, I\u0027ve got one set of problems.\u00A0 \u00A0On my 2560x1440, I\u0027ve got a different set of problems.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-28T18:02:34Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2023 06:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 28, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The1Paxman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ethat word really didn\u0026#039;t need to be there\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}